measurements.description: Approximately one thousand four hundred fifty flowers and 62 buds held well above the foliage on 68 mature and four immature up-to 36-cm inflorescences emerging from papery tan bracts; immaculately grown plant 83 cm wide, 59 cm tall, in bark in a 20-cm bulb pan; sepals and petals light chartreuse overlaid burgundy proximally, burgundy stripes, sepals forward, petals porrect; lip light chartreuse heavily overlaid burgundy; substance medium; texture matte.
